text: Collirene (also Sand Hill, Hays Hill, Hayes Hill) is an unincorporated community in Lowndes County, Alabama, United States.Collirene Topo Map in Lowndes County AL Thomas Perkins Abernethy (1890-1975), writer, historian, and educator, was born in Collirene.Alabama Writers-Thomas Perkins Abernathy ==Notes== Category:Unincorporated communities in Lowndes County, Alabama Category:Unincorporated communities in Alabama
